extendedInfo.description: Dwayne Johnson - Aka The Rock,The Great One,The Peoples champion is here with a soundboard of 24 of his best jokes! Finally the rock has come back... What is your name? It doesn't matter what your name is!!! Lay the smack down on all the cheap imitations !!! Hear the best jokes the Rock has told in front of "millions" and "millions" Rock's fans! Relive the moment when the Rock owned The Big Show, John Cena, Mankind, HHH and many more! ... and even hear the Rock speak Chinese! This is a compilation of best WWE jokes throughout the Rock's WWE career. You could practically call them electrifying! You'll slap yourself on your forehead for not downloading this app earlier!. This is one of the best compilation of The Rock's Jokes/Catch phrase in the past. The great humor you will get from this app rubs off on you! Try it now and you'll see how funny it is.
